Detailed Description

From: http://www.networksorcery.com/enp/protocol/rtp.htm.

RPT packet header content

0123 4567 0123 4567 =================== vvpx [cc] m[ pt ] [ sequenceNumber ] [ timestamp timestamp ] [ synchronization source ]

optionally: from 0 to 15 times [ contributing source ]
